These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, chinese, german, mexican
There are 4 different favourite colors: green, turquise, coral, pink
1. the person who likes pink is not to the right of the person who likes green##8
2. the person who likes pink is on the right of the brazilian##1
3. the chinese is on the left or right of the german##3
4. the mexican is somewhere to the right of the person who likes turquise##5
5. the mexican is not to the left of the person who likes pink##8
6. the person who likes coral is somewhere to the left of the chinese##5
7. the chinese is somewhere between the brazilian and the person who likes turquise##7
8. the chinese and the person who likes pink have the same parity positions##9
9. the german and the person who likes green have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | brazilian | chinese | german     | mexican |
| Pet           | coral   | pink     | turquise | green  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, march, november, february
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, drawing, sudoku, traveling
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is traveling and the person who's birthday is in march have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##8
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##5
6. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
7. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5
8. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | february     | november    | july | march    |
| Hobby      | dancing | drawing | sudoku      | traveling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, skateboarding, rowing, ice-hockey
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, avocado, mango, pumpkin
1. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the left of the person eating mango##5
2. the person eating artichoke is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rowing##5
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
6. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
7. the person eating artichoke is not to the left of the person eating avocado##8
8. the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person eating avocado have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | skateboarding    | rowing   | cycling    | ice-hockey  |
| Food       | avocado | pumpkin | artichoke | mango |

