.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, dressmaker, security-guard, software-developer
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, aristoff, game, blend
1. the prince-smoker is the dressmaker##1
2. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the game-smoker##1
3. the aristoff-smoker is somewhere to the left of the dressmaker##5
4. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
5. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the coach##1
6. the software-developer and the blend-smoker have the same parity positions##9
7. the security-guard is on the left or right of the coach##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | software-developer | security-guard | coach  | dressmaker |
| Music-Genre   | game             | aristoff          | blend | prince    |

