.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, scientific, superhero
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, parkour, lacrosse, weightlifting
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is somewhere to the left of the person watching superhero movies##5
4. the person who's sport is climbing and the person watching scientific movies have the same parity positions##9
5. the person watching superhero movies and the person who's sport is climbing have different parity positions##9
6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not to the left of the person watching animation movies##8
7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the left of the person watching animation movies##5
8. the person watching documentary movies is not to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | animation | scientific | superhero |
| Nationality   | weightlifting        | lacrosse    | climbing   | parkour |

