4. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to new-york##5
6. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |  2   |     3     |      4       |
