3. the person eating nectarine is not to the left of the person eating peach##8
4. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the person eating lemon##3
5. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far left##1
7. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
8. the person eating garlic is the person who's hobby is photography##1
9. the person eating peach and the person who's hobby is traveling have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | lemon   | peach    | nectarine | garlic    |
| Nationality   | board-games | traveling | woodworking   | photography |

